Meanwhile Trump roiled Europe by slapping 10% tariffs on eight allies for refusing to back his Greenland annexation plan. People aren't backing down. Counterprotesters in Minneapolis drowned out a tiny pro-ICE protest led by a pardoned January 6 rioter, and in Greenland nearly 25% of the capital city's population filled the streets in the country's largest protest ever.
